Class AbstractLocations

  • java.lang.Object
    • server.world.locations.AbstractLocations
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Barrows, DuelArena, Home, MageBank, PestControl, TaverlyDungeon, Tzhaar, Wilderness

    public abstract class AbstractLocations
extends java.lang.Object
    This abstracted class constructs how the classes that extends this abstract class will be formated as, each abstract void giving it's own special function for the player to conduct with.

    Dennis
